{"tid":1968284,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"本港千宗確診：留學生四分一 酒吧八分一 支那3%","createTime":"2020-04-11T14:23:57.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-11T16:38:48.000Z","uid":21470,"like":8,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"6a532d574aae922da4daaa3da49c3a98bf869791","tid":1968284,"uid":21470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-11T14:23:57.000Z","msg":"本港千宗確診中留學生佔近四分一 約八分一人涉酒吧群組<br />\n11.04.2020 22:04<br />\n<br />\n本港新型冠狀病毒確診個案達到一千宗，當中從外地回港留學生佔總數近四分一；酒吧群組相關個案亦有過百宗。據本台統計，自一月下旬本港出現首宗個案至今，輸入個案和他們的密切接觸者佔確診宗數超過六成，當中近七成確診者從英美回港，以留學生佔最多，從內地來港的個案就佔輸入個案約3%。群組個案中，佛堂、打邊爐家族及卡拉OK群組，各有超過十人染病。<br />\n<br />\n1000名病人中，有45人的病情一度達嚴重以上程度，當中4人死亡；15名重症病人治療後康復出院。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?ItemId=1280172&amp;csid=261_341\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2FPage%2FZH-TW%2Fnewsdetail.aspx%3FItemId%3D1280172%26csid%3D261_341&d=pQk%2FYDfxyk1It%2BdH9Wj1W1NDr8uFEZb%2F0ofPPvrEBCw%3D&h=1cca31cb\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?ItemId=1280172&amp;csid=261_341</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n🤒武漢肺炎民間資訊😷<br />\n<a href=\"https://wars.vote4.hk/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwars.vote4.hk%2F&d=pQk%2FYDfxyk1It%2BdH9Wj1W1NDr8uFEZb%2F0ofPPvrEBCw%3D&h=0ce7e958\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://wars.vote4.hk/</a>"},{"pid":"1067230d06d875800af6a9e1aa473751606248a6","tid":1968284,"uid":222614,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-11T15:30:27.000Z","msg":"push ...."},{"pid":"6ae56ee62e6575f63282664e66842d455b56972e","tid":1968284,"uid":165683,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-11T15:32:35.000Z","msg":"用導致既本地個案比例比較會唔會合理d"},{"pid":"e8b843435519e01d532e81e7294b10a9c49019e0","tid":1968284,"uid":66087,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-11T15:37:22.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">當中近七成確診者從英美回港</span><br />\n<br />\n即係過埋番港呢一波，香港疫情應該緩和?